79d545818c51d16ef08ba3","tid":589120,"uid":19920,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a66bdb7c7e4467a5e2e380c4850f8d6bbbd3c7c3","tid":589120,"uid":724,"like":47,"dislike":89,"score":-42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"成日話自己係民主派，但就唔比人左選擇，一定要投比你，其實你係未代表到我呢。<br />\n利申：最後投左比方小姐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"你無撚野 姓方係地下建制派 你咁都投 屌你而加連登仔係咪咁撚低質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"你個唔投香港獨立投張屌票都好呀"},{"pid":"58019cb9e66f88bf44d70c4e5cb4602cc22c8235","tid":589120,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F084237_74e818d7da05ecbe8e2e0a7ea708fdf9.png&h=6c9baf49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多撚謝販民班大愛支（尤其民主党工党同社民狗！）囉！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟德一早都知係港共專登設計既市區票倉膽！！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n「姚松炎今次做選舉工程，同我哋傳統政黨，真係好唔同，我哋唔係好慣，尤其係打開地面戰嗰班，其實一直覺得佢危。<br />\n<br />\n我哋擺街站、洗樓、去屋邨，佢哋認為唔使做好多呢啲，覺得做好網上，網上反應熱烈，就好有信心。<br />\n<br />\n即使佢哋助選團，或者幫忙嘅團體開（街）站，但好似用錯力，星期五、六下晝，喺佐敦開站，我哋一般唔會咁做，因為嗰啲係街客，去行街，唔係選民；即使開喺住宅區，有啲朝早9點後先至開，嗰啲時間，人人返晒工，開站都無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n姚松炎團隊去土瓜灣少數族裔拉票，好奇怪，或者踩單車，我哋好多人睇到，暈低咁滯。或者係我哋太傳統，唔慣咁做。<br />\n<br />\n不過泛民好多大佬，就好buy佢呢套，所以一直覺得九西呢個位好易贏，無咩危機感，其實我地做開地區嘅，睇佢唔係咁穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢種選舉工程，喺比例代表制，效果可能會比較好，今次補選只係選一個位，未必可以咁打選戰。今次投票率咁低，有好多原因，如果唔諗點樣做，下次補選，我擔心唔容易贏。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082155_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=65e18a89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F082539_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e96c93c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86cf0b0738d38a4282ed140c70a0d09b236083f9","tid":589120,"uid":82720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"本土派幾時再有人肯出嚟選呀"},{"pid":"73c68cbc161f9b4519a5d414650746f87cbbaab7","tid":589120,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f89402d83ca31b3da00678315d33b7bcb5776fb8","tid":589120,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37135c62b08ebf0f1685da1f7469da78735e4b44","tid":589120,"uid":51924,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"2afa9179a62877a592d594d1e315453907c7e191","tid":589120,"uid":79563,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"大埔大元呢D都係勁老人區<br />\n<br />\n竟然咁多人支持港獨<br />\n<br />\n其實好癲<br />\n<br />\n我都唔明點解"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"年紀大唔代表弱智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"但通常廢老都係BUY民賤聯、工聯會呢D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"一部份姐 唔係全部老人家都係廢老嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大撚把人走難落嚟 體驗過共慘黨啲仆街嘢"},{"pid":"d7fe89d97f489a3d26f422c0142b7416e33eb956","tid":589120,"uid":40779,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"一世只投天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lo